LOCUS       HaloTag                  297 aa                     UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  HaloTag7 self-labeling protein tag (297 aa) — an engineered
            monomeric haloalkane dehalogenase (from Rhodococcus DhaA) that forms
            an irreversible covalent ester bond with synthetic chloroalkane
            ligands..
